<HEADLINE> Flames Re-Sign Steve Smith </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	CALGARY, Alberta (AP) -- The Calgary Flames have signed  
unrestricted free agent defenseman Steve Smith to a two-year 
contract. 
</P>
<P>
	Smith, 36, came out of retirement a year ago and helped solidify  
the Flames' young defense. 
</P>
<P>
	Financial terms were not disclosed, but Smith is believed to  
have received a hefty raise on the $500,000 he earned last season. 
</P>
