Neither is hit. 
</P>
<P>
	-- 11:30 p.m.: In Champaign-Urbana, Ill., shots are fired at six  
men of Asian descent standing on a corner near the University of 
Illinois. One man, whose name was not released, is hit in the leg 
and was hospitalized in serious condition. 
</P>
